                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The vampire transforms into a bat.</p>\n<p>Use the options in the <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Aerial Form]{Aerial Form}</em> and <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Animal Form]{Animal Form}</em> spells as guidelines.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bat</strong> The vampire changes into a @Compendium[pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary.Giant Bat]{Giant Bat}. It gains echolocation 40 feet, a land Speed of 20 feet and a fly Speed of 30 feet, and a fangs Strike.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>@Localize[PF2E.NPC.Abilities.Glossary.ChangeShape]</p>"
                },
